MokineVeto Mobile App v1.0.0
Build Date: 2026-06-29
Platform: Android
Size: 45.2 MB
Supported: Android 12.0+

This is a placeholder APK file for testing the download functionality.
In production, this would be the compiled React Native APK from:
  eas build --platform android --auto-submit

To use: Transfer this file to Android device and install via:
  adb install mokineveto-v1.0.0.apk

Or download via browser and tap to install.
